use ../transfer/elder_combo_v5,clear
/*
ds y?_*
local toclean `r(varlist)'
foreach item in "`toclean'" {
safedrop "`item'"
}
*/
capture safedrop y 
gen y=y1+y2+y3+y4+y5+y6

global xalt2 child2  incom2  age2
global xalt1 child  incom age   
global xcat relin  incsrc mar taba alco spor exam_year sex educ
global xcont  heal  fami  depre money life
global xcont100  heal100  fami100  depre100 money100 life100
global xnew dise_o adl_o body_o iadl_o living_o commu_o
global yall y1 y2 y3 y4 y5 y6

 label define notouch 0 "非受制度影響" 1 "受制度影響"
 label value notouch notouch

xtset id year

global outposix "out_panel_oy_combo3_v5"
adopath + "D:\Activity\elderman\utils"
set linesize 255

// 清除報表: 殺掉暫存檔
local xfiles : dir report files "${outposix}_*.*"

foreach fn of local xfiles {
  erase report/`fn'
}
 
use ../transfer/elder_combo_v5,clear
/*
ds y?_*
local toclean `r(varlist)'
foreach item in "`toclean'" {
safedrop "`item'"
}
*/
capture safedrop y 
gen y=y1+y2+y3+y4+y5+y6

global xalt2 child2  incom2  age2
global xalt1 child  incom age   
global xcat relin  incsrc mar taba alco spor exam_year sex educ
global xcont  heal  fami  depre money life
global xcont100  heal100  fami100  depre100 money100 life100
global xnew dise_o adl_o body_o iadl_o living_o commu_o
global yall y1 y2 y3 y4 y5 y6

 label define notouch 0 "非受制度影響" 1 "受制度影響"
 label value notouch notouch

xtset id year



 tab2 notouch year
 xttab notouch
 

bysort id (year): egen xcount = sum(notouch)
tab xcount
safedrop xcount 
 
 eststo clear
 estpost tabstat $xcont100 $xcat $xalt1  $yall y ///
    , by(notouch) statistics(count mean sd)  columns(statistics) 

genfilename "$outposix",post(.html) pre("report/")  autoinc 
esttab using  "`r(fn)'", cells("count(fmt(%9.1f)) mean(fmt(%9.1f)) sd(fmt(%9.1f))") label nowrap  mtitle title("分年") nonumbers unstack noline html


 
  

 eststo clear
 foreach item in 2003 2007 2015 {
 estpost tabstat $xcont100 $xcont $xcat $xalt1  $yall  ///
    if year==`item', by(notouch) ///
    statistics(count mean sd)  columns(statistics) 

genfilename "$outposix",post(.html) pre("report/")  autoinc 
esttab using  "`r(fn)'", cells("count(fmt(%9.1f)) mean(fmt(%9.1f)) sd(fmt(%9.1f))") label nowrap  mtitle title("分年") nonumbers unstack noline html
}

eststo clear
eststo FEYSum: xtreg y  i.($xcat $xalt1) i.notouch##i.year,fe
eststo REYSum: xtreg y  i.($xcat $xalt1) i.notouch##i.year,re

eststo FEYSum2: xtreg y $xcont i.($xcat $xalt1) i.notouch##i.year,fe
eststo REYSum2: xtreg y $xcont i.($xcat $xalt1) i.notouch##i.year,re


foreach item in $xcont100 {
eststo FE`item': xtreg `item'  i.($xcat $xalt1) i.notouch##i.year,fe
eststo RE`item': xtreg `item'  i.($xcat $xalt1) i.notouch##i.year,re

}

foreach item in $yall {
eststo FE`item': xtreg `item'  i.($xcat $xalt1) i.notouch##i.year,fe
eststo RE`item': xtreg `item'  i.($xcat $xalt1) i.notouch##i.year,re

}

genfilename "$outposix",post(.html) pre("report/") autoinc 
esttab using `r(fn)',starlevels( * 0.10 ** 0.05 *** 0.010) r2 pr2 aic   replace label mtitle nobaselevel nolines nogaps onecell  nonumbers title("104新舊") ///
        nobaselevel refcat(1.child "子女數(base 0)" /// 
                           2.incom "收入(base 10-)" ///
                           2.age104 "年齡(base 50-54)" ///
                           1.educ "教育程度(base 不識字)" ///
                           1.incom2 "新收入(base 70-)" ///
                           1.child2 "子女數(base 0)"  ///
                           1.age2 "新年齡(base 50-59)",nolabel) 


 
hausman FEYSum REYSum
hausman FEYSum2 REYSum2
foreach item in $xcont100 {
  hausman FE`item' RE`item'
}

foreach item in $yall {
  hausman FE`item' RE`item'
}


//年齡
recode age (1/3=0)(4/5=1)(6/max=2),gen(age2)
label define age2 0 "50-64" 1 "65~74" 2 "75+"
label value age2 age2 
labellist age age2
//收入(incom)
recode incom (1/4=0)(5/7=1)(8/max=2),gen(incom2)
label define incom2 0 "70-" 1 "70~200-" 2 "200+"
label value incom2 incom2
//子女數
recode child (1/max=1),gen(child2)
label define child2 0 "無子女" 1 "有子女"
label value child2 child2 


eststo clear


//eststo FE: xtreg y $xcont100 i.($xcat $xalt2)  ,fe
//eststo RE: xtreg y $xcont100 i.($xcat $xalt2) ,re
eststo FEYSum: xtreg y  i.($xcat $xalt2) i.notouch##i.year,fe
eststo REYSum: xtreg y  i.($xcat $xalt2) i.notouch##i.year,re

foreach item in $xcont100 {
eststo FE`item': xtreg `item'  i.($xcat $xalt2) i.notouch##i.year,fe
eststo RE`item': xtreg `item'  i.($xcat $xalt2) i.notouch##i.year,re

}


foreach item in $yall {
eststo FE`item': xtreg `item'  i.($xcat $xalt2) i.notouch##i.year,fe
eststo RE`item': xtreg `item'  i.($xcat $xalt2) i.notouch##i.year,re

}


genfilename "$outposix",post(.html) pre("report/") autoinc

        nobaselevel refcat(1.child "子女數(base 0)" ///

                           1.child2 "子女數(base 0)"  ///
                           1.age2 "新年齡(base 50-59)",nolabel)
